    "description": "In fact, a short description of this game has deceived you.<br>You will be required not only to be attentive, but also to react in a timely manner, to have intelligence and a good memory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1758200/extras/891d7ef01a54b8b4f2830d6db9d664c6.avif?t=1756316699\" width=620 height=69 /></span><br><br><strong>ITRP _ Gas Prison</strong> will allow you to arrange a little test.<br>You will find yourself in a system of cells, each of which can slam and poison you with gas.<br>Keep an eye on the indicators to prevent this.<br>However, the conditions under which you will be placed will not allow you to save all cells. Some will have to be sacrificed. And there are few useless ones among them:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Some contain maps or timers.</li><li>Some stores interactive monitors for system management.</li><li>Some just has a lot of passages.</li></ul><br>The game is NOT designed to test your reflexes, reaction, accuracy or ...patience.<br>It is designed to test your attentiveness, intelligence, ability to think ahead.<br><br>Even if you need time to get used to and remember the location of the functional points, nevertheless, you will learn the detailed rules inside.",
